data.description: Location, Location, Location!  Welcome home to Willow Trace in Taylors SC. This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 full bath meticulously maintained home is situated on a .88 acre cul-de-sac  lot in a desirable neighborhood. The home features an open concept living with New vinyl plank flooring, New carpet and an updated Master bath which makes it move in ready!. The kitchen updates include an extended bar with granite countertops, new appliances, extended cabinets, as well as a beverage refrigerator. The backyard is fenced and over looks a very peaceful nature scene which is perfect for relaxing, entertaining family and friends or a place for your pets and kids to enjoy. Schedule your tour today before its SOLD!
